    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being offered as a project car or for parts salvage. It currently requires significant mechanical attention to be roadworthy, as the engine has a major leak and the transmission shifts roughly. The exterior shows heavy rust on the rocker panels, fading paint, and several noticeable dents. Inside, the upholstery is torn and the electronics are largely non-functional. It is sold strictly as-is and will likely need to be towed from the lot.",
