      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Attention all DIY enthusiasts and project lovers! This car is the ultimate fixer-upper and a fantastic opportunity for anyone looking to roll up their sleeves and get to work. While it currently needs significant mechanical attention and some TLC to get back on the road, it\u2019s a great way to own a car at a budget-friendly price. Perfect for a restoration project or a parts donor!",
