    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that balances performance with exceptional value. This unit has been maintained to rigorous standards, ensuring mechanical integrity and long-term reliability. While reflecting standard usage, the vehicle remains in commendable condition, making it a premier choice for the discerning driver who prioritizes functional excellence and proven durability.",
      "price": 31500.0,
