    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This car has been so good to me and is still in wonderful shape! It runs smoothly, looks great, and is perfect for anyone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and I\u2019d love to see it go to a great new home. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
